summary:
This mod is a compatability patch for the Chargen morphs and Chargen ECE morphs.

this will enable the same morph sliders for the Succubus Race as the vanilla races.
descriptionHtml:
This mod is a compatability patch for the Chargen morphs and Chargen ECE morphs.

this will enable the same morph sliders for the Succubus Race as the vanilla races.

Requirements:
1) Succubus Race - http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/22903
2) Chargen Extension - http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/36925
author: Tyshaunari
